This functional form implies that emission intensities decrease with rising per capita income I, as observed in the projected emission scenario. This can be interpreted as a particular version of the environmental Kuznets curve, estimated with the ECLIPSE data. We write our Kuznets-relevant income I(χ) as:4\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
