A VOLY of 2 years of per capita consumption is generally the same order of magnitude as empirical estimates based on willingness-to-pay surveys21, but we also test several alternative values in sensitivity analyses. Final (post-health) per capita consumption, cit is calculated as:24\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
